node.text:
Attention aspiring women entrepreneurs. As @mielleorganics Global Education Ambassador, I am elated to share that applications are open for Mielle's 2021 Global Education and Entrepreneurship Certificate Program through June 15, 2021! @Mielleorganics is awarding scholarships to 60 applicants to participate in their 2021 Global Certificate Program for FREE!! That's right! Access to the ABC's of developing your startup and how to acquire VC funding through the mentorship of Mielle's CEO @exquisitemo for FREE!! Applications to Mielle’s program with Rutgers University & the Newark Business Hub are available right now through June 15. Winners will be announced on June 30. To submit your application, visit www.morethanastrand.com.  

#MielleOrganics #MoreThanAStrand #morethanastrand #rutgersuniversity #applicationdeadline #keshiaknightpulliam #mielleorganics #newarkbusinesshub

node.text:
So this weekend my BFF’s threw me the most EPIC Bridal Shower weekend!! I am grateful beyond measure to have such an amazing bride squad. 

In this picture you see women who have been by my side, who have carried me, loved and supported me through it all!! 
We have picked each other up and held each other down… we definitely have stories that we will take to the grave!! I love you all Tremendously ❤️❤️❤️ 

#BCPS #ImOnACrownRoyalDetoxUntilTheWedding #FromMissToMrsWithAllMyBitches
